	measure 0_RG = ```
			IF( SUM(LTO[N_AMOUNT])<>BLANK()&&SUM(LTO[N_AMOUNT])<>BLANK(), (DIVIDE(SUM(LTO[N_AMOUNT]), SUM(LTO[C_AMOUNT]), BLANK())) -1, BLANK())
			
			```
